12 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to expand access
13 to unpaid family and medical leave and provide job-protected leave from
14 employment for reasons related to domestic violence, sexual assault, stalking,
15 bereavement, and a qualifying exigency. This bill also proposes to eliminate
16 barriers for LGBTQ+ families in accessing caregiving leave and to establish
17 reporting requirements to track the impact of expanded access.
18 An act relating to expanding employee access to unpaid leave
